a good beekeeper

01:31.424 --> 01:32.550
tries to think
like a bee!

01:32.550 --> 01:34.427
(BUZZING)

01:36.137 --> 01:38.931
What are you doing?
I'm thinking like a bee!

01:38.931 --> 01:41.392
I know! We could get stung
by radioactive bees

01:41.392 --> 01:43.644
and gain bee-themed
superpowers!

01:43.644 --> 01:47.315
Um, we don't have access
to radioactive bees.

01:47.315 --> 01:50.067
Yeah, that's what's
wrong with that plan.

01:50.067 --> 01:52.069
But we do have access
to Phineas and Ferb,

01:52.069 --> 01:53.946
and they have access
to a sorbet machine

01:53.946 --> 01:57.658
They've gotta be able to modify
it to turn people into bees.

01:57.658 --> 01:59.577
