patch ceremony?

02:55.383 --> 02:56.467
Of course!
Wouldn't miss it!

02:56.467 --> 02:57.760
See you later then.

02:57.760 --> 02:59.387
Did you know that
bees can communicate

02:59.387 --> 03:01.013
with each other
through dancing?

03:01.013 --> 03:02.723
That's really
interesting.

03:02.723 --> 03:05.267
Yes, they do
a tail wagging dance

03:05.267 --> 03:07.478
to alert each other
to the source of food.

03:07.478 --> 03:08.521
The waggle explains...
Okay, let's see.

03:08.521 --> 03:12.400
Setting targets.
Fireside Girls.

03:12.400 --> 03:13.651
And that should do it!

03:13.651 --> 03:15.486
(BEEPING)
Here we go!

03:15.528 --> 03:17.154
PHINEAS: Mind giving me a hand with...
In a minute.

03:17.154 --> 03:19.991
So, to continue,
the figure-eight dan...

03:21.158 --> 03:22.243
Aw!

03:22.243 --> 03:24.286
And we are back.

03:29.291 --> 03:32.044
Fireside Bees!
Follow your noses!

03:32.044 --> 03:33.170
(SNIFFING)

03:33.170 --> 03:35.172
ALL: That way!

03:35.172 --> 03:38.259
Mmm. Much better.

03:38.259 --> 03:40.177
Now that my lips
are taken care of,

03:40.177 --> 03:43.305
I can tell you about my
beautifully evil plan.

03:43.305 --> 03:45.516
Bad doggie! Okay, sit.

03:46.308 --> 03:47.435
That's better.

03:47.435 --> 03:52.314
Slowly moves closer and we
cross-dissolve to my thoughts.

03:52.314 --> 03:54.316
<i>Behold,
the humble bee hive.</i>

03:54.316 --> 03:57.445
<i>A massively ordered society,
just like our own.</i>

03:57.445 --> 04:01.323
<i>Observe, u young grub being fed
moss quantities of royal jelly,</i>

04:01.323 --> 04:02.575
<i>which will make her larger,</i>

04:02.575 --> 04:05.536
<i>and eventually she
will become their queen.</i>

04:05.536 --> 04:08.539
<i>So logic dictates that
if I were to consume</i>

04:08.539 --> 04:10.332
<i>massive amounts
of royal jelly,</i>

04:10.332 --> 04:11.542
<i>then I would grow
forty times bigger</i>

04:11.584 --> 04:13.335
<i>and live forty times longer</i>

04:13.335 --> 04:16.213
<i>and eventually be crowned
Queen of the World!</i>

04:16.213 --> 04:17.464
